HEALTH_DESCRIPTION_63: Ilmahaagu wuu dhashay! Hambalyo! Waxaad isbitaalka u timid wakhti fiican.
HEALTH_DESCRIPTION_64: Naso si fiican, ilmahaaga noocso oo la xidhiidh bixiyahaaga caafimaadka! 10 maalmood ee ugu horreeya weli waa khatar weyn. Raadi calaamadahan khatar ah adiga. Qandho, dhiig idinka soo baxa ama daad macaan oo ka soo baxa farjiga, qallafsanaan.
